Package Summary 
Package Description
it.polimi.ingsw
Classes that implement the Santorini game.
it.polimi.ingsw.client
Classes that implement the core functionalities of the Santorini client.
it.polimi.ingsw.client.clientstates
Abstract classes defining the possible states of the Client.
it.polimi.ingsw.client.reducedmodel
Classes used by the client to keep a local representation of the state of the game.
it.polimi.ingsw.client.ui
Classes that implement the UI.
it.polimi.ingsw.client.ui.cli
Classes that implement the CLI user interface.
it.polimi.ingsw.client.ui.gui
Classes that implement the GUI user interface.
it.polimi.ingsw.client.ui.gui.guicontrollers
Classes that implement the JavaFX controllers for the Santorini GUI client.
it.polimi.ingsw.client.ui.gui.guicontrollers.elements  
it.polimi.ingsw.client.ui.gui.utils
Utility classes used by the Santorini GUI client.
it.polimi.ingsw.server
Classes that implement the core functionalities of the Santorini server.
it.polimi.ingsw.server.controller
Classes that implement the view of the MVC pattern used by the Santorini server.
it.polimi.ingsw.server.model
Classes that implement the model of the MVC pattern used by the Santorini server.
it.polimi.ingsw.server.model.actions
Classes representing the actions that can be performed during a turn of the game.
it.polimi.ingsw.server.model.board
Classes representing the elements of the Santorini board.
it.polimi.ingsw.server.model.gods
This package contains the implementation of the Gods of Santorini.
it.polimi.ingsw.server.model.turnevents
This package allows the game to interact with the gods in order to allow them to modify the standard game logic, depending on their specific powers.
it.polimi.ingsw.server.model.turnstates
Classes representing the states of the state pattern used to handle the progress of the Turn.
it.polimi.ingsw.server.model.workers
Classes to represent the players' workers.
it.polimi.ingsw.server.view
Classes that implement the view of the MVC pattern used by the Santorini server.
it.polimi.ingsw.utils
Utility classes shared between the client and the server of Santorini.
it.polimi.ingsw.utils.config
Utility classes to read and parse the configuration for Santorini.
it.polimi.ingsw.utils.i18n
Utility classes to handle the internationalization (i18n) of Santorini.
it.polimi.ingsw.utils.networking
Classes handling the communication over the network between client and server.
it.polimi.ingsw.utils.networking.transmittables
Classes representing the messages exchanged over the network.
it.polimi.ingsw.utils.networking.transmittables.clientmessages
Classes representing the messages sent from the client to the server over the network.
it.polimi.ingsw.utils.networking.transmittables.servermessages
Classes representing the messages sent from the server to the client over the network.
it.polimi.ingsw.utils.observer
Classes that implement the observer pattern.
it.polimi.ingsw.utils.structures
Classes that implement general purpose data structures.
